      *  check division --- is nylok code in process master for this part#
     C                     EXSR @DIVCH
     C           *IN30     IFEQ *ON
     C                     GOTO #ECHK3
     C                     ENDIF
      *
      *
TCHK3C                     MOVE A2BHB1    WWBHB1           INTERNAL PART
